    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The event or condition of an office, post, or tenancy, usually a political office, post, or tenancy, being, becoming, or falling vacant. Vacancies occur by the voluntary act of the incumbent, by circumstances such as a death, or by compulsion.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
